<paragraph blockId="4.[157,1010,202,623]" pageId="4" pageNumber="340">Distance between alternate hydrocladia 800–900 Stem and hydrocladia, width 88–96 distance between alternate hydrocladial hydrothecae 440–496 Apophysis, depth 72–96 Hydrotheca</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[157,1010,202,623]" pageId="4" pageNumber="340">length, diaphragm to margin 328–400 width of margin 160–184 width at diaphragm 72–88 Nematotheca</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[157,1010,202,623]" lastBlockId="4.[151,1436,692,749]" pageId="4" pageNumber="340">
length 68–84 width at margin 40–48 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,693,716]" pageId="4" pageNumber="340">Distribution</emphasis>
. This is the second record of 
<taxonomicName box="[657,905,692,716]" class="Hydrozoa" family="Lafoeidae" genus="Zygophylax" kingdom="Animalia" order="Leptothecata" pageId="4" pageNumber="340" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="crozetensis">
<emphasis box="[657,905,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="340">Zygophylax crozetensis</emphasis>
